result.execSummary:
The defendant Nicole J. Brownell was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Nicole J. Brownell is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Nicole J. Brownell was found guilty of Possess/Illegally Obtained Prescription, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 450.11(7)(h).
